anceled desc = context canceled'，同时cartservice自身出现'System.IO.IOException: The client reset the request stream'和'Error reading message'错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务在调用cartservice时遇到大量gRPC超时和连接中断问题，包括context canceled和transport is closing错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多个frontend实例报告'could not retrieve cart: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = timed out waiting for server handshake'和'could not retrieve cart: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = transport is closing'\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现：\n\n**主要异常模式**：\n1. **cartservice服务异常**：cartservice-1出现I/O异常和消息读取错误\n2. **gRPC连接中断**：frontend与cartservice之间的gRPC连接频繁中断\n3. **超时问题**：服务间握手超时和传输关闭错误\n\n**影响范围**：\n- 所有frontend实例（frontend-0、frontend-1、frontend-2）都受到影响\n- 购物车功能完全失效，无法添加商品到购物车或查看购物车\n- 错误集中在06:11-06:21期间，高峰期出现在06:11-06:13\n\n**根因推测**：cartservice服务可能出现了资源耗尽或网络连接问题，导致无法正常处理frontend的gRPC请求。", "trace_analysis_findings": "{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->frontend\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用自身（CartService/GetCart和CartService/AddItem）的延迟从正常时的约4-25ms飙升至异常时的约50-60ms，延迟倍数高达1000倍以上。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用productcatalogservice的GetProduct接口延迟从正常时的约9-11ms增加到异常时的约12-15ms，延迟倍数约为1.2-1.5倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice调用redis的HGET操作延迟从正常时的约1.5ms增加到异常时的约49.6ms，延迟倍数约为32倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice调用shippingservice的ShipOrder接口延迟从正常时的约14.4ms增加到异常时的约52.4ms，延迟倍数约为3